<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                        Hans Stark und <expan>F<ex>ricz</ex></expan> Wolmeyr, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, von iren und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gesellschaft, auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r,</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n,</ex></expan> wie in <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        gesagt sey worden, daz in etwievil hab und kauffmanschaft ümb ew in
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> gegend aufgehalten und
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> worden sey; dabey Cristan, genant
                                <expan>Venedig<ex>er,</ex></expan> ir diener sey gewesen, der in die
                        herheim braht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> solt.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        darümb ewr gnade yendert anrüffen werden, daz in
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedig hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne gnediklich beweisen wölle. Als
                        etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi an Georii.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> graf Hansen von Görcz, graf
                                <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Ortemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Görgen von <expan>Awersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, ritter, czu
                                <expan>Awersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> gesessen.</ab>
